<h1><center>This Week In<br>Pacific Fleet History</center></h1>
<title>This Week In Pacific Fleet History</title>
</center>
<hr>
<br>
<h2>August 15, 1945:<br>V-J (Victory Over Japan) Day</h2>
The last air strike of the war is launched at 4:15 a.m. by the carriers of Task Force 38.  News of the Japanese surrender leads to the recall of a second wave already approaching the Japanese coast.<br>
<br>
<hr>
