<h1>Mrs. Zlatoper Receives a<br>
Distinguished Service Award</h1>
<title>Mrs. Zlatoper Receives Award</title>
<hr><br><br><br>
<img src="mrszdod.gif" alt="Mrs. Zlatoper Receives Award" align="right" height=278 width=400>
<strong>(November 7, 1996)</strong> -- "My wife Barry has been my soul 
mate for 26 years, has been with me through the successes on this journey and I wouldn't be here without her, in fact I wouldn't want to be here without her," said Admiral Zlatoper during his farewell speech.  Mrs. Zlatoper received the Department of Defense Distinguished Public Service Award for her years of service to the Navy.  Pictured handing the award to Mrs. Zlatoper is Admiral Jay Johnson, Chief of Naval Operations. (Official U.S. Navy Photo by JO1 Robert Benson)<br><br>
