<li>HMAS Perth (DDG-38) (Guided Missile Destroyer)
<li>HMAS Success (AOR-304) (Replenishment Oiler)
<li><a href="ffg3fact.htm">HMAS Sydney</a> (FFG-03) (Guided Missile Frigate)
