<h1>RIMPAC 96<BR>Bi-Lateral Force:<BR><br>JDS NATSUSIHO (SS 584)</h1>
<br><br><br>
<title>JDS NATSUSIHO (SS 584)</title>
<hr>
<h2>JDS NATSUSIHO (SS 584)</h2>
<img src="ss584co.gif" alt= "" align=left align=middle height=167 width=135>
<h2>Commander Masakazu Kaji</h2>
