<hr>
<h1>.50 Caliber Machine Gun</h1>

The Browning M2 .50 Caliber Machine Gun is an automatic, recoil operated, air-cooled machine gun with adjustable headspace and is crew transportable with limited amounts of ammunition over short distances.<br>
By repositioning some of the component parts, ammunition may be fed from the right or left side.  A disintegrating metallic link-belt  is used to feed the ammunition into the weapon.<br>
The "50 cal" has a back plate with spade grips, trigger, and bolt latch release.  This weapon may be mounted on ground mounts and most vehicles as an antipersonnel or antiaircraft weapon.<br>
It is equipped with a leaf-type rear sight, flash suppressor and a spare barrel assembly.<br>
<h3>
Specifications</h3>
<pre>
Maximum effective range..........................1.13 miles
Maximum range....................................4.22 miles

Rate of fire
Cyclic...........................................550 rounds per minute

Weight
Gun..............................................84 pounds
M3 tripod........................................44 pounds

Caliber..........................................50
Length...........................................61.42 inches
Builder..........................................Saco defense
</pre>
<hr>
