<html>
<body background="chalk.jpg">
<img src="rimpac3.gif" alt= "" align=left align=middle height=145 width=190>
<img src="sealusmc.gif" alt= "" align=right align=middle height=145 width=151>
<br><center><h1>RIMPAC 96<BR>Multi-National Force:<br><br>11th Marine Expeditionary Unit</center></h1>
<hr>
<h1>CH-46 Sea Knight</h1>
The Mission of the CH-46 Sea Night is to provide all weather, day/night, night vision goggle (NVG) assault transport of combat troops supplies and equipment during amphibious and subsequent operations ashore.  Troop assault is the primary function and the movement of supplies and equipment is secondary.<br>
Additional tasks are:
<ul>
<li>combat and assault support for evacuation operations and other maritime special operations
<li>over water search and rescue augmentation
<li>support for mobile forward refueling and rearming points
<li>aeromedical evacuation of casualties from the field to suitable medical facilities
<li>and medium-range tactical recovery of aircraft and personnel (TRAP)
</ul>

<h3>Specifications</h3>
<pre>
Payload...................................22 troops with aerial gunners
                                          Medical evac for 15 litter
                                          patients & two attendants
                                          5,000 pounds max.
                                          external load
Maximum Speed.............................166 miles per hour
Range.....................................151.8 miles
Crew......................................Normal -- 4
                                          Combat -- 5
Gross Weight..............................24,300 pounds
Length....................................45 feet, 8 inches
Height....................................16 feet, 8 inches
Rotor Diameter............................51 feet
Armament..................................Two M-2 (.50 caliber) or
                                          M-60 (7.62mm) machine guns
Manufacturer..............................Boeing Vertol Company
</pre>
<hr>
<h5>Source - 11th MEU</h5><br>
