<html><head><title>INNOVATE</title></head>

<body><p>
<img align=bottom src="/innovate/innovat2.gif" alt="INNOVATE"><br>
<p>
Welcome to "<a href="/innovate/innovate_form.htm">INNOVATE</a>"!!  We at CINCPACFLT have many new challenges to meet.  
We are interested in finding new ways for our Navy to meet these challenges 
without sacrificing either our operational effectiveness or the quality of 
life of our people.  We need some new ideas in PACFLT.  There are over 
140,000 officers and sailors in the Pacific and a significant number of 
civilians as well.  We are sure that there are a large number of ideas, big
and small, from this talented group of professionals that can point us new 
ways for us to do our job more effectively and more affordably.  We are asking
you to help get these ideas via the "<a href="/innovate/innovate_form.htm">INNOVATE</a>" Program.
<p>
"<a href="/innovate/innovate_form.htm">INNOVATE</a>" is focusing on ideas that address three primary questions:  
(1)  What are we doing now that we could be doing better or more affordably?
(2)  What are we doing now that we should not be doing?
(3)  What are we not doing now that we should be doing?
<p>
"<a href="/innovate/innovate_form.htm">INNOVATE</a>" does not replace any existing hotlines, request masts EEO programs, 
etc.  It is not intended as a complaint forum.  It is intended as a different
mechanism to surface and evaluate different approaches to issues and problems
without the more formal, and lengthy structure of point papers and staffing.  Effective use of "<a href="/innovate/innovate_form.htm">INNOVATE</a>" can provide a unique opportunity to improve the quality of CINCPACFLT.  We encourage and welcome your participation.
<p><hr>
<center>
<img src="/scripts/WWWpac.exe?innovate+style:WWWpacLg;yellow;blue+f:1+fc:grey" align=bottom>  Visitors since 5/10/96.
</center>
</body></html>
