<DOCHDR>
http://www.thompson.com:80/tpg/person/wage/wagedec2.html 207.226.10.52 19970117180042 text/html 7069
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.3.1 ID/15792
Message-ID: <af025d20.14479@207.226.10.52>
