<html> <title> ADA Compliance Guide Specialty Chapters </title>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/tpg/gif/tpgpattern.gif">

<center><IMG SRC="/tpg/person/able/ablehead.gif" alt="ADA Compliance
Guide"></center>
<P>
<h2> ADA Compliance Guide Specialty Chapters</h2>
<body>

In addition to the <i>ADA Compliance Guide</i>, chapters are available providing
in-depth discussions of how the ADA affects specific industrial and public
activities. Chapters provide practical compliance information, including
<a href="/tpg/person/able/ableself.html">self-evaluations</a> of initial and
ongoing compliance efforts and <a href="/tpg/person/able/abletips.html">tips</a> about
applying the rules in the "real world." <P>

With your <i>Guide</i> subscription, you may purchase as many of the following 
chapters as you need for a complete ADA picture. Chapters are available for:<P>

<UL>
<LI>Banks<P>

<LI>Colleges and universities<P>

<LI>Courts and correctional facilities<P>

<LI>Elementary and secondary schools<P>

<LI>Hotels<P>

<LI>Police and fire departments<P>

<LI>Public works and housing<P>

<LI>Retail and grocery stores</UL><P>

The chapters may not be purchased separately, but only in addition to the <i>Guide</i>.
Each chapter costs $59.<P>

</body> 

